claim.claim-text:
1. A radio transmission device for transmitting data through a radio line, comprising:
data inputting means for inputting transmission data;
data compressing means for compressing the inputted transmission data;
compressed data storing means for storing the compressed data temporarily;
data transmitting means for reading the compressed data from the compressed data storing means to transmit the compressed data through the radio line; and
throughput judging means for judging a throughput in the radio line.

2. A radio transmission method for transmitting data through a radio line, comprising the steps of:
inputting transmission data;
compressing the inputted transmission data;
storing the compressed data temporarily;
transmitting the compressed data through the radio line; and
judging a throughput in the radio line.

3. A radio receiving device for receiving data through a radio line, comprising:
data receiving means for receiving compressed data through the radio line;
output data storing means for storing the received data temporarily by a first-in first-out method;
data decompressing means for reading data from the output data storing means by a first-in first-out method to decompress the data;
data outputting means for outputting the data decompressed by the data decompressing means; and
throughput judging means for judging a throughput in the radio line.

4. A radio receiving method for receiving data through a radio line, comprising the steps of:
receiving compressed data through the radio line;
storing the received data temporarily by means of a first-in first-out method;
reading the temporarily stored data by means of a first-in first-out method to decompress the data;
outputting the decompressed data; and
a throughput judging step for judging a throughput in the radio line.

5. A radio transmission device for transmitting data through a radio line, comprising:
an input device for inputting transmission data;
a compressor for compressing the inputted transmission data;
a storage for storing the compressed data temporarily;
a transmitter for reading the compressed data from the storage and transmitting the compressed data through the radio line; and
a judging device for judging a throughput in the radio line.

14. A radio receiving device for receiving data through a radio line, comprising:
a receiver for receiving compressed data through the radio line;
a storage for storing the received data temporarily using a first-in first-out method;
a decompressor for reading data from the storage using a first-in first-out method to decompress the data;
an output device for outputting the data decompressed by the decompressor; and
a judging device for judging a throughput in the radio line.
